I along with two friends tried Thai Chili 2 Go because we wanted some good Thai food and fast. I ordered the Pad Thai, the others order the Pad Siew... one with chicken and the other beef. We all were disappointed in our meals so we decided to try one anothers, but honestly we could not tell the difference. Each dish was mushy and had way too much sauce... all we could taste was sugar.  We will most likely not be coming back

